FBIS3-14217 "drnes057_n_94007" FBIS-NES-94-057 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 LEBANON Security Forces Crack Down in Beirut, al-Biqa' NC2403065194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0530 GMT 24 Mar 94 NC2403065194 Beirut Radio Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] The Lebanese Army and the Internal Security forces have intensified security measures in accordance with the Lebanese Government decision. They have deployed mobile and foot patrols and set up fixed and mobile checkpoints in Beirut's southern suburb. The army and Internal Security Forces are continuing the security measures taken in the Kasrawan area. A NATIONAL NEWS AGENCY correspondent reports that the security forces on the al-Biqa' plain, helped by Syrian Arab forces units, yesterday evening began implementing similar security measures in the area, especially in Ba'labakk and al-Hirmil.
